      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_B7526A80-216B-0135-3317-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To view a course, click the name of the course [1]. If a course lets students self-enroll, you can join the course at any time by clicking the <strong>Join this Course </strong>button [2]. However, you can view the course first and enroll in the course home page.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
